Invocation Name: pie facts
des: Pie number facts delivers you random facts about all things with numbers. Whether you want some random knowledge about a specific number, date, or year, you can ask Pie number facts about it. If you don't have a number in mind, just launch the skill and Pie number facts will choose a number for you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
